# .claude/settings.json is committed & team-shared — it holds only secret-free config
# (hooks, customInstructions, non-secret env such as model routing). Secrets and machine-
# specific permissions belong in .claude/settings.local.json (ignored via the managed block
# below and by *.local.* above) or an OS env var (e.g. AZURE_DEVOPS_PAT).
# .claude/hooks/check-settings-secrets.cjs blocks a secret from reaching the shared file at
# both write-time (PreToolUse) and commit-time (pre-commit).

# === ai-assisted-development (managed) ===
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/security-checkpoint.json
.claude/code-review-checkpoint.json
.claude/file-cache.json
.claude/dream-init-state.json
memory/health.html
CodeReviews/*
!CodeReviews/code-review-ledger.md
security/*
!security/security-ledger.md
dynamic-scan/*
!dynamic-scan/dynamic-scan-ledger.md
token-analysis/
prod-readiness/
temp/
.claude/plugin-path.txt
# === end ai-assisted-development ===
